### Example 1.9: Physical Constants

The `phys/constant` verb retrieves standard physical constants (speed of light, Planck's constant, etc.).

```scheme
(define c (phys/constant 'c))   ; speed of light
(define h (phys/constant 'h))   ; Planck constant

(list 'c c 'h h)
```

